==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: rén fēi shèngxián, shú néng wúguò

===Etymology===
Literally: People are not sages, who can be without error?

===Proverb===
'''[[人]][[非]][[聖賢]]，[[孰]][[能]][[無過]]'''

# Nobody's perfect.

===Alternate forms===
[[人非圣贤，孰能无过]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[人]][[非]][[聖賢]]，[[誰]][[能]][[無過]]

